We finally got
a piece of the pie

00:23.575 --> 00:25.956
Fish don't fry
in the kitchen

00:26.095 --> 00:28.683
Beans don't burn
on the grill

00:28.821 --> 00:31.238
Took a whole lot of tryin'

00:31.376 --> 00:33.964
Just to get up that hill

00:34.103 --> 00:36.519
Now we're up
in the big leagues

00:36.657 --> 00:39.108
Gettin' our turn at bat

00:39.246 --> 00:41.593
As long as we live,
it's you and me, baby

00:41.731 --> 00:43.319
There ain't nothin' wrong
with that

